To share data from child to parent using @ViewChild() decorator, we need to follow the below steps.

Step1: Create a child component and parent component.
(In post component.ts we have created a variable name childMessage Variable) 

Step2: Import ViewChild from @angular/core.
(In parent component.ts (app) we have imported ViewChild from @angular/core. then import post component then afterViewInit)

 step 3: inside the html file print using string interpolation    